<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"smc_player_progress_bar compact-progress-bar\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"player_time_slider_base compact-player-slider-base ltr_direction\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"player_time_slider compact-player-slider\"><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"compact-info-bottom clearfix\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"compact-timeline\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"song_current_progress compact_current_progress\">0:00<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"player_duration_sep compact_duration_sep\">&#47;<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"song_duration compact_song_duration\">0:00<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"compact-controls\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-step-backward mpfe-compact-bottom-player-icon\"><\/i>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-step-forward mpfe-compact-bottom-player-icon\"><\/i>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-list-ul mpfe-compact-list\"><\/i>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"swp-compact-playlist swp-playlist-popup\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"compact-close-playlist-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"swp-compact-playlist-inner-container swp-playlist-popup-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"swp-compact-playlist-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"swp_music_player_entry compact-player-entry clearfix\" data-mediafile=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Best-Practices-for-Cross-Platform-Marketing-Management.mp3\">\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"swp_song_details player_entry_left\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"play_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-play before_song compact_bs\"><\/i>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"player_song_name transition3\" data-albumname=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"entry_duration mpfe_fix_lh\"><\/span>\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fff38f6 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fff38f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6b69aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b6b69aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>With the advancement of technology, the increased dependence on a global network has made it imperative for marketing campaigns to be launched and sustained on several different platforms. This makes campaigns necessary and very complicated for businesses regardless of their size.<\/p><p>In this modern, complex environment, however, success for the marketer is only guaranteed by devising strategies that reflect coherent and consistent messages integrated with precise data and thoughtful conclusions across all channels. This informative publication presents the fundamental best principles ensuring efficient cross-platform marketing management and simplifies the complexities of modern-day digital marketing.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-accdc9c all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"accdc9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1. Unified Data Management<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4ef8e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b4ef8e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To begin with, every effective cross-platform marketing strategy has a common characteristic of customer data management that enables a complete picture of all customers. Gaining all the data that originates from emails, social media, website analytics, paid search, and the like helps one comprehend the customer journey fully. This broader perspective provides better focus to strategies, enhances customization, and aids in decision-making.<\/p><p>A Customer Data Platform (CDP) must be part of this process because it helps innovate with all the touchpoint data available. A CDP centralizes an organization\u2019s customer data, lifting it from numerous disconnected platforms. This integrated data can be used to build customer profiles, enhance audience segmentation, and activate data in different marketing channels.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75b0bb0 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"75b0bb0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Data Governance and Customer Tracking<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a6d0a97 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a6d0a97\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Data governance policies should be enforced to uphold data accuracy and integrity across platforms. Marketers can use unique identifiers, such as a customer ID or email address, to follow specific customers through various channels. This way, marketers will be able to fully understand how customers engage with the brand even without using the same platform.<\/p><p>Applications such as <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/hubspot\/\">HubSpot Marketing Hub<\/a>, Segment, and Salesforce Customer 360 are indispensable in this noble quest for data unification. These technologies possess strong integration features, enabling linking multiple data clouds to curate one accurate customer data repository.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e5904b all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6e5904b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Consistent Messaging and Branding<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1ab1e6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1ab1e6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To foster brand awareness and credibility, it is vital to maintain the same voice and message across all platforms. Consumers involving themselves with the brands more than they used to, have many touchpoint possibilities; therefore, consistency means that the target audience will experience an integrated brand, regardless of the channel employed. Take your time to design an overarching brand style guide that applies to all the communication channels that you have at your disposal.<\/p><p>This should comprise information on brand elements like tone, visual and verbal pots, message hierarchies, and message use per channel. This way, you shall have set out a walking document that every team member and outside stakeholders can use in their communication strategies.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1bdc6f6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1bdc6f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Consistent-Messaging-and-Branding-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17564\" alt=\"Consistent Messaging and Branding\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Consistent-Messaging-and-Branding-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Consistent-Messaging-and-Branding-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Consistent-Messaging-and-Branding-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Consistent-Messaging-and-Branding.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32e367f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"32e367f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2. Content Strategy and Tools for Consistency<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd69746 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cd69746\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Come up with a content calendar to help strategize and integrate content across the channels while ensuring that an appropriate story is sustained across every message despite changing the message content for different channels. This should also focus on when content is placed, where, and the audience of that content. For instance, LinkedIn&#8217;s approach and content may differ from that of Instagram in that the delivered message might be and should be different. At the same time, the values represented by the brand remain intact.<\/p><p>Tools such as ActiveCampaign, which runs coordinated campaigns across email, SMS, and other means of communication, will come in handy to avoid mixed messages in any of the channels used. Hootsuite or Sprout Social will also come in handy for curating and managing social media content to ensure consistent social media communication where the tone and content of the message are relevant to the brand. To ensure consistency across visual aspects, applications like Canva or Adobe Creative Cloud assist in designing and coordinating brand visuals across different media and formats.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0fedb9f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0fedb9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3. Integrated Campaign Planning<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cfd3933 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cfd3933\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In any marketing campaign, planning the workload for cross-platform marketing is crucial. This method allows one to capitalize on each channel&#8217;s advantages without losing the customer-oriented focus.<\/p><p>First, define the campaign goals and key performance indicators to help achieve the interrelated business objectives. These goals should be SMART (specific, measurable, achievable, relevant, and timed) and reflect your strategy for all platforms.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e983f5e all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e983f5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">4. Cross-Platform Coordination and Attribution<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fcbf83d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fcbf83d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This exercise makes it easy to discover prospects for inter-platform co-activities and deliver the right messages at every stage of the customer\u2019s interaction with the service offered. Identify the touchpoints of your brand\u2019s customer and factor in the customer\u2019s journey on all available channels and platforms.<\/p><p>Use cross-platform attribution models to gauge the contribution of each channel to conversion and the entire campaign\u2019s effect. Multi-touch attribution helps you understand the role of various touchpoints in driving conversion, allowing you to plan better and optimize marketing interventions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f89550 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6f89550\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tools for Campaign Management and Analytics<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-520bb1b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"520bb1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Get team collaboration software such as Asana, Trello, or Monday.com and use it to organize your work across several teams and channels. These programs will assist with managing activities, deadlines, and resources to ensure the smooth execution of the cross-channel activities.<\/p><p>Tools such as Google Analytics 4, which supports advanced cross-platform tracking, should be used for analytics and attribution. For B2B marketing, solutions like Dreamdata and Bizible will help multi-touch attribution data for your campaigns.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e8697b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7e8697b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Tools-for-Campaign-Management-and-Analytics-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17565\" alt=\"Tools for Campaign Management and Analytics\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Tools-for-Campaign-Management-and-Analytics-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Tools-for-Campaign-Management-and-Analytics-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Tools-for-Campaign-Management-and-Analytics-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Tools-for-Campaign-Management-and-Analytics.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0aee34b all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0aee34b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Real-Time Performance Monitoring and Optimization<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1973203 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1973203\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>One of the primary benefits of digital marketing services is, without a doubt, the ability to monitor and act on campaign performances instantaneously. This can increase your marketing campaigns&#8217; efficiency and help you quickly respond to the market or customers\u2019 behaviors. You can have a range of designs and concepts, which are better expressed in proper figures. They include graphical and pictorial representations and timelines on quite several slides. This involves presenting sports images and graphs of many hustings with different campaigns in several dashboards. Such dashboards are beneficial in a campaign since they come up with metrics such as engagement level, conversion level, ROI, and an estimate of the costs of acquiring customers through all the channels.<\/p><p>Ensure you have a defined cycle for assessing and improving performance based on real-time insights and information. This could be strategy sessions at the beginning of each day for prominent campaigns or weekly digital marketing strategy meetings for ongoing campaigns. Focus on actions taken on all marketing channels individually while looking at the odds for the performance level and results in that range.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-79e5ece all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"79e5ece\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">A\/B Testing and Tools for Optimization<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0247e6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d0247e6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Emphasize A\/B Testing to enhance effectiveness on each platform and improve your marketing strategy. Include different variables like ad text, pictures, landing pages, email headlines, and the like for each campaign, as every platform requires specific customization. Also, a winning tactic for one platform may not necessarily translate across all terrains, making further upgrades necessary for respective channels.<\/p><p>Google Analytics is a valuable web and mobile tool for measuring web and cross-platform usage. At the same time, Tableau or Power Business Intelligence can be used to develop unique dashboards and data visualizations from different data sources. For more comprehensive testing and experimentation, especially for A\/B testing on other channels, I suggest looking into software such as Optimizely or VWO (Visual Website Optimizer).<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-792cd93 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"792cd93\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">5. Personalization at Scale<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1ab89b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e1ab89b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18100b9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"18100b9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>When it comes to data use, creating such experiences across different platforms is bound to translate to higher levels of engagement with the business and increased conversion rates. McKinsey management consulting services have found that the cost of personalization in marketing can yield five to eight times more returns on investment, plus increase sales by over 10%.<\/p><p>The first step is clustering your audience by behaviors, likes or dislikes, and other demographic features such as age or gender. This segmentation aims to guide the implementation of dynamic content strategies in which messages are customized to specific individuals via email, web, and advertising channels, among other channels. For instance, an organization could develop various email content provided for new clients and already loyal clients or display multiple website banners for a user based on his or her browsing history.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c0f578 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5c0f578\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-7\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">6. Retargeting and Predictive Techniques<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-342be51 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"342be51\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4049aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c4049aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>Employ retargeting techniques to enhance brand consistency as users hop from one platform to the next, optimizing each touchpoint of the consumer journey. For instance, a customer \u201cleaving\u201d without placing an order on your e-commerce web page may come across related products in a social network that are \u201cadvertised\u201d on the web, where they are browsing other products instead.<\/p><p>Predictive analytics and machine learning algorithm applications allow business owners to anticipate what customers tend to prefer, allowing them to provide advance-focused experiences. This may include suggesting and cross-selling items before customers make their final purchases based on previous history or timing differences in sending messages to customers before they are likely to be signed into the system.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3013ca0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3013ca0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Retargeting-and-Predictive-Techniques-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17566\" alt=\"Retargeting and Predictive Techniques\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Retargeting-and-Predictive-Techniques-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Retargeting-and-Predictive-Techniques-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Retargeting-and-Predictive-Techniques-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Retargeting-and-Predictive-Techniques.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f6e35e all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9f6e35e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tools for Personalization<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ac3e83 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6ac3e83\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Aimed at maximizing engagement, Adobe Target supplies extensive tools for personalization across web and mobile devices and content optimization at scale. Marketo focuses more on B2B personalization and spelling out account-based marketing tactics, such as designing the audience to companies and specific people within those companies. To implement omnichannel personalization, products such as Dynamic Yield and <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce\/\">Salesforce<\/a> Interaction Studio are recommended to help seamless personalization across all customer touchpoints. Partnering with experts like <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mountainise<\/a> ensures these tools are integrated effectively to maximize customer engagement and personalization outcomes.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64b215d all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"64b215d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-8\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">7. Compliance and Data Privacy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7b9694 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e7b9694\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Adhesion to evolving data protection laws such as the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), as well as developing regulations in a given market, is an integral part of the job description for modern marketers. Non-adherence to these rules can lead to hefty fines and tarnish your brand\u2019s image.<\/p><p>Establish an overarching data management system that governs customer data acquisition, storage, and use across all marketing touchpoints. This policy should include effective measures for data management, access restrictions, and the duration of keeping such information.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd0e349 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cd0e349\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-9\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">8. User Consent and Internal Data Practices<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78554ca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"78554ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Always ensure that data collection and usage policies are clear and available to users at all times and on all platforms. Effective systems that help gain user consent for data collection and enable them to retain control of their privacy easily are also essential. One such system is preference centers, where users determine the category or amount of communication or the use of their information.<\/p><p>Carry out Internal controls and evaluate your firm\u2019s current data practices to comply with the existing governing policies and be ready for any future shifts in the governing laws. This activity will include assessing the data collection methods and procedures, their storage systems, and information sharing with outside parties<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a215a42 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a215a42\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-10\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">9. Tools for Privacy Management<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-76e9d35 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"76e9d35\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0932726 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0932726\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>The privacy principles by design are embedded and enacted within the marketing technology stack. The latter facilitates better compliance and addresses customers\u2019 fears. Companies like OneTrust aid in resolving various privacy-related challenges by offering tools for consent management and privacy impact assessment. For this reason, Securiti.ai provides data governance and compliance services that give you a 360-degree view of your data. This platform is helpful for organizations that process massive amounts.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db32f21 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"db32f21\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-11\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d6bf76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1d6bf76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In order to manage marketing effectively on various platforms, it is crucial to take a strategic view whereby data, messaging, and customer experiences are cut across all platforms. Observing these practices and adopting the necessary tools to achieve effective marketing campaigns that bear success is advisable. Mind that one has to keep learning and adapting. With the emergence of new platforms and technologies and changing consumer behavior patterns, it is vital to remember your cross-platform marketing strategy. Consider revising your approaches occasionally, and do not hesitate to change them to keep your heads above water.<\/p><p>With an emphasis on the management of data as a whole, the promotion of a single branding message, the development of a single marketing plan from the start, the adjustment of efforts on the fly, making the message to the customers relevant, and adhering to all laws and regulations, you will be able to deal with cross-platform marketing challenges and fulfill your corporate goals. Take a comprehensive approach and have the necessary means at your disposal. You will be able to provide your customers with an uninterrupted and pleasing interaction at all points, which will enhance their loyalty, increase conversions, and accelerate the growth of the business in the long run.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c3fb220\" data-id=\"c3fb220\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-f6ea9e5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f6ea9e5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-7241ae8\" data-id=\"7241ae8\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9554eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d9554eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Latest WhitePaper<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88014a4 elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-2 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-posts--thumbnail-top elementor-posts__hover-gradient elementor-widget elementor-widget-posts\" data-id=\"88014a4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;cards_columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_columns_tablet&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;cards_columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_row_gap_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&qu